        {
            "title": "外國去年淨買入的美國股票翻逾一倍 中國大陸則連續三年拋售",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><span class=\"news-dateline\">【彭博】--</span> 儘管美國總統唐納德·川普的關稅驚攪了市場也使企業前景蒙上陰影，但外國投資者2025年買入的該國股票仍是前一年的兩倍有餘。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">美國財政部周三公佈的數據顯示，去年來自境外的淨買入金額攀升至7201億美元，比2024年的3075億美元成長了134%，創出了至少十年來最高增速。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">不過，中國大陸連續第三年淨賣出美國股票，2025年拋售的金額高達341億美元。只有科威特的賣出規模更甚 —— 365億美元。</p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-3b9bbf21-aa29-3be5-b8fb-f59f726b1ad9-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">對美股的趨之若鶩與去年興起的「去美化」情緒形成了鮮明對比。當時川普的關稅威脅令全球貿易岌岌可危，同時投資者也擔心白宮會削弱聯儲會的獨立性。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">推薦閱讀：海外2025年淨買入1.6萬億美元美資 中國逆勢大拋2000多億</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">「至少就股票而言，所謂‘去美化’是誇大了，」 Acadian Asset Management LLC高級副總裁兼投資組合經理Owen Lamont說。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">他還說道：「我們看到的是美國例外論。對美國科技股的大肆追捧似乎還在繼續。」</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">原文標題Foreigners Buy US Stocks at Decade-High Rate Despite Tariffs (1)</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">More stories like this are available on <a class=\"link\" data-ylk=\"slk:bloomberg.com;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.bloomberg.com\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">bloomberg.com</a></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">©2026 Bloomberg L.P.</p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E5%A4%96%E5%9C%8B%E5%8E%BB%E5%B9%B4%E6%B7%A8%E8%B2%B7%E5%85%A5%E7%9A%84%E7%BE%8E%E5%9C%8B%E8%82%A1%E7%A5%A8%E7%BF%BB%E9%80%BE-%E5%80%8D-%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E5%A4%A7%E9%99%B8%E5%89%87%E9%80%A3%E7%BA%8C%E4%B8%89%E5%B9%B4%E6%8B%8B%E5%94%AE-205312820.html",
            "pub_date": "2026-02-20 05:49:46",
            "source": "yahoo_finance_asia",
            "kind": 1,
            "language": "zh-HK"
