            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "川普關稅影響下 美國對華貿易逆差收窄至21年來最低",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit\"><img alt=\"Bureau of Economic Analysis\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"758\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/trw1kgLPfslPCwT2IZrsvg--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTc1OA--/https://media.zenfs.com/en/bloomberg_chinese_traditional_757/b7f41bf45beea9aad9d5c3833d5da5cd\" width=\"960\"/><figcaption class=\"text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere\" style=\"max-width:960px\">Bureau of Economic Analysis</figcaption></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><br/></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><span class=\"news-dateline\">【彭博】--</span> 在川普大規模的關稅重塑全球貿易格局之際，美國2025年對華年度<a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link\" data-ylk=\"slk:貿易逆差;sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link;itc:0\" href=\"https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/tag/貿易逆差\">貿易逆差</a>收窄至逾二十年來的最低水平，而對墨西哥和越南的貿易逆差則擴大至創紀錄水平。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">美國商務部周四公佈的數據顯示，對華貿易逆差為約2020億美元。加拿大對美國的貿易順差也收窄，原因是儘管川普在首個任期內與加方談判達成《美墨加協定》，但兩國之間的交易仍受到衝擊。</p><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit\"><img alt=\" \" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"758\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/W14LjvupzTW_iQCz8RdHqw--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTc1OA--/https://media.zenfs.com/en/bloomberg_chinese_traditional_757/1ca3c646103118a82eb6e100e7308b03\" width=\"960\"/><figcaption class=\"text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere\" style=\"max-width:960px\"> </figcaption></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">與此同時，台灣去年對美貿易順差接近翻倍，原因是在人工智能相關領域的蓬勃發展推動下，美國的半導體和電子產品進口激增，而台灣的出口商受益於關稅豁免。</p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-05789cf4-5f2c-3d35-9913-68a136f140b0-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">川普在其第二個任期一直依賴貿易關稅來減少對外國商品的依賴，鼓勵國內投資，並扭轉數十年來美國製造業就業人數持續下滑的局面。根據彭博經濟研究，美國進口商品的實際關稅稅率目前為13.6%，這一數字高於自1940年代以來至2025年之前的任何時期。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">自川普第一任期以來，中國對美貿易順差一直在收窄。當時，中美之間的貿易戰促使中國越來越多地通過墨西哥和越南等第三方來轉口出口。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">推薦閱讀：美國12月份貿易逆差擴大 全年錄得1960年以來最大逆差之一</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">原文標題Trump’s Tariffs Send US Trade Deficit With China to 21-Year Low</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">--聯合報導 Vince Golle.</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">More stories like this are available on <a class=\"link\" data-ylk=\"slk:bloomberg.com;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.bloomberg.com\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">bloomberg.com</a></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">©2026 Bloomberg L.P.</p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E5%B7%9D%E6%99%AE%E9%97%9C%E7%A8%85%E5%BD%B1%E9%9F%BF%E4%B8%8B-%E7%BE%8E%E5%9C%8B%E5%B0%8D%E8%8F%AF%E8%B2%BF%E6%98%93%E9%80%86%E5%B7%AE%E6%94%B6%E7%AA%84%E8%87%B321%E5%B9%B4%E4%BE%86%E6%9C%80%E4%BD%8E-180829977.html",
            "pub_date": "2026-02-20 03:25:06",
